                <li>other uses.</li>
            </ol>
            <p>If you submit personal information for publication on our website, we will publish and otherwise use that
                information in accordance with the license you grant to us.</p>
            <p>Your privacy settings can be used to limit the publication of your information on our website and can be adjusted
