                <li>to the purchaser (or prospective purchaser) of any business or asset that we are (or are contemplating)
                    selling; and</li>
                <li>to any person who we reasonably believe may apply to a court or other competent authority for disclosure of
                    that personal information where, in our reasonable opinion, such court or authority would be reasonably
                    likely to order disclosure of that personal information.</li>
            </ol>
            <p>Except as provided in this policy, we will not provide your personal information to third parties.</p>
            
            
